---
// Footer 组件 - 页脚
---

<footer class="border-t border-white/10 mt-20 relative z-10 bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-600"></span>
      <span class="font-display font-bold">SYS.LOG</span>
    </div>
    <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-mono">
      &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} SYS.LOG Engineering Blog.
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-6">
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors hover-trigger flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-mono" title="RSS">
        RSS
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors hover-trigger flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-mono" title="GitHub">
        GITHUB
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>